"content": "<h2>Negotiation between peoples</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:23\">GEN 21:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:31-Luke14:32\">LUK 14:31–14:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:6\">JOS 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:4\">JOS 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:2\">1SA 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:12-2Sam3:13\">2SA 3:12–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:19\">1KI 15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:23\">2KI 18:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa36:8\">ISA 36:8</a></p>\n<h2>Negotiation in the buying of land</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:8-Gen23:9\">GEN 23:8–23:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:4\">RUT 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:24\">2SA 24:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:8\">JER 32:8</a></p>\n<h2>Negotiation in the setting of wages</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:15\">GEN 29:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:27\">GEN 29:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:32\">GEN 30:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:10-Judg17:11\">JDG 17:10–17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:6\">1KI 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:2\">MAT 20:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:14-Matt26:15\">MAT 26:14–26:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:10\">MRK 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:4\">LUK 22:4</a></p>\n<h2>Negotiation for personal safety</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:12-Josh2:13\">JOS 2:12–2:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:12-Judg15:13\">JDG 15:12–15:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:8\">1SA 20:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:15\">1SA 30:15</a></p>",
